#~ "You can enter <userinput>Jouyou</userinput> and <userinput>Jinmeiyou</"
#~ "userinput> to get Kanji not in a regular grade but in those groups."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Вы можете вводить <userinput>Jouyou</userinput> и <userinput>Jinmeiyou</"
